de.ityx.mediatrix.data

Class DetailsFilter

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.ityx.mediatrix.data.ErpsData
      • de.ityx.mediatrix.data.DetailsFilter
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IErpsData, Serializable

    public class DetailsFilter
extends ErpsData
implements Serializable
    Describes the regular expressions in the filter. The regular expressions are applied to header, subject, content or keywords and bound with the "and" or "or" conjunction. The filter matches the informations to take the decision whether the filter actions are to be applied to the incoming question or not.
